---
source: tests/cli.rs
expression: "help_output(& [\"tools\", \"list\", \"--help\"])"
---
List installed tools and their versions

Prints each installed tool version from the cache (name, version, source, install date) plus the baked default versions for managed tools that are not installed. Never touches the network.

Usage: hpds tools list [OPTIONS]

Options:
  -v, --verbose
          Show more detail (underlying commands, tool names)

  -q, --quiet
          Suppress all output except errors

      --no-color
          Disable colored output

      --config <PATH>
          Use this config file instead of discovering hpds.toml

  -h, --help
          Print help (see a summary with '-h')
